**Header blockquote** (date / repo / local path / branch / HEAD) + **TL;DR**: 24-state EKF fuses at a
*delayed* time horizon; an output predictor propagates the newest IMU forward to "now" for low-latency
attitude/vel/pos; sensors enter via uORB → per-sensor delay/ring-buffer; a selector promotes 1 of N
instances. NED throughout; biases are *delta* biases.

