   - 7.2 Output-topic table — the 22 `Publish*` methods → topic → key fields → rate.
8. **EKF selector & runtime noise adaptation (high level + diagrams)**
   - 8.1 `EKF2Selector` — embed `_selector.svg`; N instances → gyro/accel error accumulators +
